{"tid":1112040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男童彈出彈入　馬路亂咁衝　司機怒斥︰遲早出事","createTime":"2019-04-17T08:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T08:57:31.000Z","uid":225464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e6db2d61f6a8da6b400dc0ebe6b3c9f41adad9dd","tid":1112040,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:08:08.000Z","msg":"男童彈出彈入 馬路亂咁衝 司機怒斥︰遲早出事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PexkT1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PexkT1&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdArwDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=3fcfbab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PexkT1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190417/photo/bkn-20190417153123374-0417_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190417155612\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190417%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190417153123374-0417_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190417155612&h=4efe21da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車都唔睇就照衝！<br />\n<br />\n有司機行經粉嶺聯昌街時，由於左右兩側均泊滿車輛，不時又有途人在馬路上步行，故司機均緩緩直駛，呈得小心翼翼。其時，一名手持飲料的男孩忽然從路旁的車隙中衝出，「彈吓彈吓」地橫過馬路。所幸當時車速緩慢，未釀成意外。"},{"pid":"02f23dd32d1124307f5144e6d69b434f1c116e32","tid":1112040,"uid":35014,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:09:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"853cdca4c2173640b657e07a905ea4e8873ad831","tid":1112040,"uid":122134,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aTRZB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaTRZB.gif&h=5b9f1f3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"906a3b46338748fc4ee05b8cb778b5219942db72","tid":1112040,"uid":63909,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"無證據都想講<br />\n係大陸人多"},{"pid":"4b13d8e56ba4c47f234bce390bae7df500a99740","tid":1112040,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"妓者知唔知彈出彈入點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/no